nodes.text: Sulituans were a species with nautilus-like heads and shells with long tentacles that served as arms and legs. They lived on Archae Teuthis. The Podracer Tzidik Wrantojo was a Sulituan.
"Sulituan" is "nautilus" spelled backward, letter for letter. "Architeuthis" is the genus name of the Giant Squid.
